Description:

Established in the best tradition of the great hits Age of Empires and Age of Kings, 
it is worthy of a place in the collection of any, even the most advanced player! Nine 
absolutely different peoples, each of them - the unique skills and talents over. 
Epic battles in the atmosphere of ancient legends and tales. Here are fighting even the 
ancient gods of Greece, Egypt and the Scandinavian countries. After all, this is the era 
when the flow of blood is shed, and people worship the great inhabitants of heaven. 
Era of myths and legends!

The publication also includes the official continuation of the game - The Titans. 
Players will take control of an entirely new race and create the most destructive 
creature - a giant battle of titanium! With his participation battle acquire, 
unprecedented scope and sweep to the ground the enemy hordes became more 
interesting and much more pleasant.

Age of Mythology: Extended Edition is an adapted version of the 
project under the current system.

The Extended Edition includes:
Age of Mythology
Age of Mythology: The Titans
Golden Gift Campaign.
